      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This week, Starbucks workers won union victories in Pittsburgh, Pa.; Philadelphia, Pa.; Knoxville, Tenn ;Portland, Ore.; Chicago, Ill; Independence, Mo.; Los Angeles, Calif.; Louisville, and Buffalo, N.Y. In total, as Matt Bruenig ",
            "type": "text",
